<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="balance-v">balance <strong><em>v</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /'bæləns/    美 /'bæləns/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-vt-vi">1.★ <strong>vt &amp; vi (使) 保持平衡；(使) 均衡：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The hospital needs to <strong>balance the budget</strong> each year.
医院每年都要使预算保持平衡。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Hobbies help people balance between work <strong>and</strong> play<strong>balance between </strong>
业余爱好有助于人们平衡工作和娱乐。</p></div></div>